{
  "stem": "3638.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're not allowed to have any furs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a hard life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't as good as before, but nobody starved.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Still I say, I still my-- I mean, in our family, we did not starve.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where can you live?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can't live.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is all-- you can't-- you couldn't live from Krakow to the-- to Warsaw, you couldn't live.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to have papers, permission.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't board a train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't board a train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My auntie was living about just like from here to Katoomba, [INAUDIBLE], which is not far from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could not board a train without the permission.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German soldier were on the station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you have to have a-- a pass.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they introduced the-- the, what you call it, in the first few months they introduce it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to have, what you call-- what is it called?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Armband, yes, with the star.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A little bit later, little bit later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like that, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "White with a blue-- blue Magen David.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Star of David, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could not-- if they catch you without it, you would be in a big trouble.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While we're in Krakow, you didn't have to have papers when you were in this surrounding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You say you leave Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How can you leave Poland?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't live anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all the borders were closed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were talking about building the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did eventually, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the last thing was they did it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because-- because before they build the ghetto, the Jewish people used to live everywhere in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Platz, ?] in Padgorze, anywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was Judenrat, they called it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
